57
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:50,960
So early?

58
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,400
I-It’s not early.

59
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,040
You said you are going to look up

60
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,320
