the hospital for new dressing.

76
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,480
How about I give you a lift?

77
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:17,200
The same way, anyway.

78
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:19,720
It’s pretty early.

79
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,440
I’m used to it.

80
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,720
OK, thanks.

81
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:39,600
Dr. Xu.

82
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:44,640
Dr. Xu.

83
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:45,800
You’re off duty.

84
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:46,480
Bye-bye.

85
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,080
Dr. Xu,

86
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:53,280
