93
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,320
Director Shao.

94
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,080
Are you waiting for me?

95
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:04,800
No.

96
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:10,000
