97
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,440
You should have put on
more clothes, Director Shao.

98
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,400
It’s OK. I drove here.

99
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,240
Are you feeling cold?

100
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,440
I’m OK.

101
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,280
Director Shao.

102
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:23,840
Morning.

103
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:24,920
Morning.

104
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,480
What’s the plan for tonight?

105
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:27,520
Tonight?

106
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:30,840
Nothing.

107
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:32,080
I have a party at home tonight.

108
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,040
You will come, right?

109
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,000
Oh, here you are.

110
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:39,960
